[3905.051439, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KA\bA\r\u001b[K\u001b[H\u001bM       other expansions, unless they have been quoted themselves.\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[21;1H\r\u001b[K\u001b[7m Manual page bash(1) line 1834 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
[3905.071499, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KA\bA\r\u001b[K\u001b[H\u001bM       present  in  the  original  word, not ones resulting from one of the\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[21;1H\r\u001b[K\u001b[7m Manual page bash(1) line 1833 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
