[5841.047352, "o", "\u001b[H\u001bM       If the substitution appears within double quotes, word splitting and\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[20;1H\r\u001b[K\u001b[7m Manual page bash(1) line 2059/6908 31% (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
