[5841.111613, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KA\bA\r\u001b[K\u001b[H\u001bM       quoted form, escape the inner backquotes with backslashes.\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[20;1H\r\u001b[K\u001b[7m Manual page bash(1) line 2057/6908 31% (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
