[5841.810426, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K       The old format \u001b[1m$[\u001b[4m\u001b[22mexpression\u001b[24m\u001b[1m] \u001b[22mis deprecated and will  be  removed  in\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page bash(1) line 2051/6908 31% (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
