[5853.272824, "o", "\u001b[H\u001b[2J\u001b[H\u001bM       Utilities portion of the IEEE  POSIX  specification  (IEEE  Standard\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM       \u001b[1mBash  \u001b[22mis intended to be a conformant implementation of the Shell and\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM       corporates useful features from the \u001b[4mKorn\u001b[24m and \u001b[4mC\u001b[24m shells (\u001b[1mksh \u001b[22mand \u001b[1mcsh\u001b[22m).\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM       commands read from the standard input or from a file.  \u001b[1mBash \u001b[22malso in‐\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM       \u001b[1mBash \u001b[22mis an \u001b[1msh\u001b[22m-compatible command language interpreter that  executes\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM\u001b[1mDESCRIPTION\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM       Inc.\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM       Bash  is  Copyright  (C)  1989-2022 by the Free Software Foundation,\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM\u001b[1mCOPYRIGHT\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM       \u001b[1mbash \u001b[22m[options] [command_string | file]\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM\u001b[1mSYNOPSIS\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM       bash - GNU Bourne-Again SHell\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM\u001b[1mNAME\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[H\u001bM\u001b[4mBASH\u001b[24m(1)                   General Commands Manual                   \u001b[4mBASH\u001b[24m(1)\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[20;1H\r\u001b[K\u001b[7m Manual page bash(1) line 1/6908 0% (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
